data.description: WELCOME TO 54 CALDWELL!  This beautiful 3 bed 2.5 bath home features an open floor plan with a welcoming Foyer Entry, a well-appointed Kitchen, Dining Area, Great Room with fireplace, and Bonus Room.  This Gorgeous Kitchen boasts granite counters, tile backsplash, breakfast bar, pantry, ample cabinets and countertops, and stainless steel appliances to include a French-door refrigerator.  Adjacent to the kitchen is the Laundry Room and Hall Tree for Drop Zone area when entering from the garage.  The Owner' Suite is located on the first floor and features a tray ceiling and a lovely wooded view of the back yard.  The bathroom has a spacious vanity, garden tub with tile surround, separate shower w/seat, private toilet, and large walk-in closet.  Upstairs there are two additional bedrooms, a large Bonus Room with niche area, and an oversized step-in linen closet.  Relax in the fenced backyard and enjoy your view of the woods from your deck or by the firepit.  Come take a look today.
